<span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><strong><span style="font-size: 18pt;" class="bbc_size">Notas sobre PHP</span></strong></span><br /><br /><strong>Operaciones con cadenas:</strong><br />strlen($string); &lt;- contar cuantos caracteres tiene el string.<br /><br />substr(string, posicion inicial[, cantidad]); &lt;- devuelve una subcadena de la cadena, formada por los caracteres a partir de la posición indicada como la inicial (opcional, la cantidad de caracteres a devolver despues de la posición inicial).<br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code">$cadena1=&quot;jeje es neta&quot;;<br />$cadena2=substr($cadena1, 5); // $cadena2 contendrá el valor de &quot;es neta&quot;</code><br />str_replace(expresión original, expresión a reemplazar, $cadena); &lt;- buscará en $cadena la primera variable y la reemplazará por la segunda, devuelve una nueva cadena modificada.<br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code">$cadena1=&quot;jeje es neta&quot;;<br />$cadena2=str_replace(&quot;jeje es&quot;, &quot;es hilarante amigo, es verídico,&quot;, $cadena); // $cadena2 contiene el valor &quot;es hilarante amigo, es verídico, neta&quot;</code><br />strtolower &lt;- Pasa de mayúsculas a minúsculas.<br />strtoupper &lt;- Pasa de minúsculas a mayúsculas.<br />substr_count &lt;- Cuenta el número de apariciones de una subcadena.<br />ucwords &lt;- Hace que la primera letra de cada palabra de la cadena se convierta a mayúscula.<br /><br /><strong>Expresiones regulares</strong><br /><br />ereg()<br />ereg_replace()<br />eregi()<br />eregi_replace()<br /><br />Nota: estas funciones luego de compilarlas el server me advirtió que son &quot;deprecated&quot;, es decir, parece que ya son muy viejas y están como obsoletas.<br /><br />Mas sobre expresiones regulares: <a href="https://alanchavez.com/como-usar-shell_exec-en-php-de-manera-segura/" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">https://alanchavez.com/como-usar-shell_exec-en-php-de-manera-segura/</a><br /><br /><strong>Una nota sobre funciones</strong><br />En PHP, uno puede crear funciones, colocarle variables de entrada y asignarles valores por defecto, algo que al parecer es único en PHP...<br /><br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code">function speak($entrada = &quot;jeje es neta&quot;)<br />{<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;return $entrada;<br />}<br />echo speak(&quot;lolnada!&quot;); // esto devuelve &quot;lolnada!&quot;<br />echo speak(); // esto devuelve &quot;jeje es neta&quot;</code><br /><strong>Funciones de interés</strong><br /><br />gettype(): devuelve el tipo de una variable<br />otras de comprobación: is_array(), is_bool(), is_float(), is_integer(), is_null(), is_numeric(), is_object(), is_resource(), is_scalar(), is_string()<br />var_dump(): muestra el tipo y el valor de una variable, especialmente interesante con los arrays<br /><br />htmlspecialchars(): impide que se interpreten los caracteres especiales de HTML<br /><br /><strong>Variables Predefinidas</strong><br /><br />$GLOBALS, $_SERVER, $_GET, $_POST, $_COOKIES, $_FILES, $_ENV, $_REQUEST, $_SESSION<br /><br /><strong>Fecha y hora (date &amp; time)</strong> (<a href="http://www.w3schools.com/php/php_date.asp" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">W3schools</a>)<br /><br />date(&quot;Y/m/d&quot;), date(&quot;Y-m-d&quot;), date(&quot;Y&quot;), date(&quot;l&quot;)<br />d: day (01-31)<br />m: month (01-12)<br />Y: year<br />l: day of week<br /><br />date(&quot;h:i:sa&quot;)<br />h: 12-hour format (01-12)<br />i: minutes (00-59)<br />s: seconds (00-59)<br />a: am or pm<br /><br />Fecha y hora regional:<br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #0000BB">&lt;?php<br />date_default_timezone_set</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"America/New_York"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br />echo&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"The&nbsp;time&nbsp;is&nbsp;"&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">date</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"h:i:sa"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /></span><span style="color: #0000BB">?&gt;</span></span><br /></code><br />Fecha y hora personalizadas:<br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code"><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #0000BB">&lt;?php<br />$d</span><span style="color: #007700">=</span><span style="color: #0000BB">mktime</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #0000BB">11</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">14</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">54</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">8</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">12</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">2014</span><span style="color: #007700">);&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #FF8000">//$d=strtotime("10:30pm&nbsp;April&nbsp;15&nbsp;2014");<br /></span><span style="color: #007700">echo&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"Created&nbsp;date&nbsp;is&nbsp;"&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">date</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"Y-m-d&nbsp;h:i:sa"</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">$d</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /></span><span style="color: #0000BB">?&gt;</span></span><br /><br /><span style="color: #000000"><span style="color: #0000BB">&lt;?php<br />$d</span><span style="color: #007700">=</span><span style="color: #0000BB">strtotime</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"tomorrow"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br />echo&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">date</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"Y-m-d&nbsp;h:i:sa"</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">$d</span><span style="color: #007700">)&nbsp;.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"&lt;br&gt;"</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br /><br /></span><span style="color: #0000BB">$d</span><span style="color: #007700">=</span><span style="color: #0000BB">strtotime</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"next&nbsp;Saturday"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br />echo&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">date</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"Y-m-d&nbsp;h:i:sa"</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">$d</span><span style="color: #007700">)&nbsp;.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"&lt;br&gt;"</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br /><br /></span><span style="color: #0000BB">$d</span><span style="color: #007700">=</span><span style="color: #0000BB">strtotime</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"+3&nbsp;Months"</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br />echo&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">date</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"Y-m-d&nbsp;h:i:sa"</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #0000BB">$d</span><span style="color: #007700">)&nbsp;.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"&lt;br&gt;"</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br /></span><span style="color: #0000BB">?&gt;</span></span><br /></code><br /><strong>Manipulación de archivos</strong> (<a href="http://www.w3schools.com/php/php_file_open.asp" class="bbc_link new_win" target="_blank">W3schools</a>)<br /><br /><div class="codeheader">Código: <a href="javascript:void(0);" onclick="return smfSelectText(this);" class="codeoperation">[Seleccionar]</a></div><code class="bbc_code">fopen(&quot;myfile.txt&quot;, &quot;r&quot;);</code>r &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Open a file for read only</strong>. File pointer starts at the beginning of the file<br />w &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Open a file for write only</strong>. Erases the contents of the file or creates a new file if it doesn&#039;t exist. File pointer starts at the beginning of the file<br />a &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Open a file for write only</strong>. The existing data in file is preserved. File pointer starts at the end of the file. Creates a new file if the file doesn&#039;t exist<br />x &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Creates a new file for write only</strong>. Returns FALSE and an error if file already exists<br />r+ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Open a file for read/write</strong>. File pointer starts at the beginning of the file<br />w+ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Open a file for read/write</strong>. Erases the contents of the file or creates a new file if it doesn&#039;t exist. File pointer starts at the beginning of the file<br />a+ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Open a file for read/write</strong>. The existing data in file is preserved. File pointer starts at the end of the file. Creates a new file if the file doesn&#039;t exist<br />x+ &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>Creates a new file for read/write</strong>. Returns FALSE and an error if file already exists
